data.description: Welcome to the country! This updated 3 bedroom, 1 and a 1/2 bath home checks all the boxes. Open floor plan with main floor laundry. Large 30x40 ft barn with an upper level just waiting for someone to put to use. The 1 acre lot even includes an area set up for an RV with a power pole and pad. Additional features of the home include: updated kitchen, home generator, newer furnace, replacement windows, and all the appliances stay with the home. Conveniently located just west of Lansing. Give Geno a call at 269-986-3031 and lets make this your new home.
